    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly ride that's ready to work? This dependable vehicle is in honest, fair condition and has served its previous owners well! While it shows some cosmetic wear and tear from its years on the road, it remains a solid choice for anyone needing reliable transportation at a great price. It's a character-filled car that's ready for many more miles!",
