    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint, showroom condition and has been preserved with the utmost care. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish, free of any chips or scratches, and the interior remains in a pristine state with no signs of wear. Mechanically, it is in perfect working order, having been maintained to the highest standards and stored in a climate-controlled environment. A buyer can expect a vehicle that looks, feels, and drives exactly as it did when it first left the dealership floor.",
      "price": 48500.0,
