      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an exemplary specimen of automotive engineering, maintained in showroom condition. This vehicle exhibits a flawless exterior finish paired with a meticulously preserved interior, reflecting a history of fastidious care and climate-controlled storage. Every mechanical system has been rigorously vetted to ensure performance that mirrors its original factory specifications. We invite discerning buyers to inspect this peerless offering, which represents a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle of such uncompromising caliber.",
