      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Offered here is a truly exceptional vehicle in absolute showroom condition. This car has been climate-control garaged and meticulously cared for, presenting with a flawless exterior finish and a factory-fresh interior that still carries that new-car aroma. The paint is deep and reflective, free of any chips or swirls, while the leather upholstery remains supple and entirely free of wear. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, with every service performed exclusively at authorized service centers and a complete set of records to prove it. For the buyer seeking a pristine, collector-grade example that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line, this is the one.",
      "price": 48500.0,
